Connections to ESP32
LORA RFM95W

    3.3V --> 3.3V
    GND --> GND
    RESET --> 14
    NSS --> 5
    SCK --> 18
    MOSI --> 23
    MISO --> 19

L298N Motor Driver

    D0 --> 27
    D1 --> 26
    D2 --> 25
    D3 --> 33

Motors:

    Motor Right --> Motor Driver
    Motor Left --> Motor Driver

Power:

    Battery --> Motor Driver

TP4056

    + --> Vin (place a switch between TP4056 + and Vin)
    - --> GND
    B+ --> Battery +
    B- --> Battery -
